    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You weave necromantic magic into your arrow. The creature hit by the arrow takes a number of additional d6 equal to your Intelligence modifier (minimum of 1) Necrotic damage. The target must also succeed on a Constitution saving throw, or the damage dealt by its weapon attacks and Unarmed Strikes is halved until the start of your next turn.</p><p>After you reach 15th level in this class, when the creature takes the Attack action it can only make one attack until the start of your next turn.</p>",
